Home








Trusted Leader in Textile Technology

Safety Components is a global market leader in technology driven fabric solutions 
for first responders, military, outdoor, and other high performance textiles. 
A division of the International Textile Group (ITG), Safety Components has been 
manufacturing textile fabrics for over 100 years at its plant in Greenville, 
South Carolina.

Headquartered in Greensboro, NC, ITG employs over 6,000 people worldwide making 
it one of the largest and most reliable textile companies in the world.










