Stop, Drop, Rock 'n' Roll

 Over the past ten years, Stop, Drop, Rock 'n' Roll has played an important part in
 helping us honor America's fallen firefighters. It is a chance for firefighters to give
 back to the fire service and have fun at the same time. Through a small donation
at the door and life auction you have the opportunity to help the National Fallen
Firefighters Foundation honor and support the families of firefighters who have
died in the line of duty.    










